# SandboxApp Architecture

## System Registration

```
pg::CreateApplication()  [Sandbox2D.cpp]
  ├── Sandbox::Create()                       (delegates to pg::Application::Create())
  ├── World::RegisterSystem(sbx::ConfigLoaderSystem)
  └── World::RegisterSystem(sbx::SampleUISystem)
```

Neither system shares a write or inframe-add dependency with the other, so the ECS topological sort
preserves registration order: ConfigLoaderSystem always executes before SampleUISystem.

## Boot Sequence (Frames 1–3)

```
Frame 1
  ConfigLoaderSystem  reads Assets/App/Config.json
                      defers SampleUIConfigSingletonComponent
  SampleUISystem      returns early — ResourceMapSingletonComponent not yet flushed

Frame 2
  ConfigLoaderSystem  no-op (SampleUIConfigSingletonComponent already exists)
  SampleUISystem      both guards pass; defers SampleUISingletonComponent + OrthographicCameraComponent
                      emits LoadLayoutEvent → UIControlSystem loads SandboxUI.json next frame

Frame 3+  (steady state)
  ConfigLoaderSystem  no-op
  SampleUISystem      emits DrawQuadInFrameEvent, DrawSpriteInFrameEvent, DrawStringInFrameEvent × 2
                      renders ImGui "Settings" panel (live-edit of quad/text transforms)
```

## Steady-State Data Flow

```
Assets/App/Config.json
  └── sbx::ConfigLoaderSystem
        └── SampleUIConfigSingletonComponent
              └── sbx::SampleUISystem
                    ├── SampleUISingletonComponent    (mutable scene state, ImGui-editable)
                    ├── OrthographicCameraComponent   (scene camera; 1280x720, ReactsToInput=true)
                    ├── DrawQuadInFrameEvent          (flat coloured quad each frame)
                    ├── DrawSpriteInFrameEvent        (sub-texture sprite, matched by UI entity UUID)
                    └── DrawStringInFrameEvent × 2    (static text + animated elapsed-time clock)

Data/Assets/App/UI/SandboxUI.json  (loaded once via LoadLayoutEvent)
  └── pg::UIControlSystem
        └── BaseComponent + ImageComponent + TextComponent entities
              └── pg::UIRenderSystem
                    └── DrawUIQuadInFrameEvent, DrawUIStringInFrameEvent
```

## Key Files

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `Code/SandboxApp/Sandbox2D.cpp` | Entry point — CreateApplication() and system registration |
| `Code/SandboxApp/Sandbox/ConfigLoaderSystem.cpp` | Reads Config.json, creates SampleUIConfigSingletonComponent |
| `Code/SandboxApp/Sandbox/SampleUISystem.cpp` | Scene init and per-frame draw event emission |
| `Data/Assets/App/Config.json` | UUID references for UI elements, font, and layout |
| `Data/Assets/App/UI/SandboxUI.json` | Root UI layout definition (two children: image + text widget) |
